-- =============================================================================
-- FOREX CLIENT
-- forexclient
-- v0.7.0-EURUSD-METATRADER-LITE
--
-- Purpose:
--   Trading-terminal style client for the Oracle/Kraken EUR/USD forexserver.
--
-- This build:
--   - safe self updater using startup.new/startup.old
--   - removes the old top info block
--   - adds clickable timeframe tabs: 1m, 5m, 15m
--   - requests server-side candle history for each timeframe
--   - renders joined candles with neutral/no-change candles flat
